            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/219">Stefano</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> de <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/126">Sancti
                            Bartholomei</orgName> sito locho <placeName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#places/281">Sextinghe</placeName> concede in livello a
                                <persName><name ref="Ildebrandus">Ildibrando</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Donatus">Donato</name></persName> germani filii
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Ildebrandus">Ildibrandi</name></persName> (…)
                        medietatem de <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casis et cassinis</rs>
                        seo <rs key="#Casalini/fundamenta">chasalinis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Curtes">curtis</rs> et <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiis</rs> sive
                        rebus meis illis <rs key="#Demesnes">donichatis</rs> et massariciis (…) quam
                        habeo in loco <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Demesnes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Casalini/fundamenta #Churches"
                            ref="#places/321">Tacte</placeName> cum de meam portionem ex integra de
                            <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/164">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName> medietatem, in loco <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions">Chapilliani</placeName> seu in <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions">Trigungnani</placeName> adque a <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions">Butro</placeName> et in loco <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions">Ferruni</placeName> sive in <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Churches" ref="#places/322">loco ubi dicitur a
                            Sancto Stefano</placeName> sive cum de meam portione de <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/165">Sancti
                            Stefani</orgName> cum de meam portione medietate de <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curte</rs> de <placeName key="#Curtes" ref="#places/323"
                            >Padule</placeName> adque de meam portione medietate de <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> chui vocabulo est <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/166">Sancti Andree</orgName> et in <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions">Aquatiche</placeName> et in <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/324">Verliani</placeName> et in
                            <placeName key="#Landed_possessions">Vergniani</placeName> et in
                            <placeName key="#Landed_possessions">Gritaio</placeName> adque in
                            <placeName key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/326"
                            >Chastianu</placeName> seu et in loco <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions">Fabbri</placeName> et in <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/327">Monte Giachuni</placeName>
                        et in <placeName key="#Landed_possessions">Sequerciana</placeName> vel per
                        aliis locis et vochabulis con tutte le loro dipendenze, sicut iam obvenit
                        per <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">cartula offersionis</rs> in prefatus
                        monasterio da <persName><name ref="Gherardus">Gherardo</name></persName>
                        filio bone memorie <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName> et
                        in cartula ipsa continere videtur; eccetto integram meam portionem de
                        integre quatuor <rs key="#Mansi">masce</rs>, una que est posita ha
                            <placeName key="#Mansi" ref="#places/326">Castiianu</placeName> et iam
                        recta fuit per <persName><name ref="Suverellus">Suverello</name></persName>
                        massario; alia est posita ha <placeName key="#Mansi">Quercito</placeName>;
                        tertia est posita haf.<placeName key="#Mansi">Fabbri</placeName>; quarta est
                        posita ha <placeName key="#Mansi">Piro Grosso</placeName>. I livellari si
                        impegnano a versare all’abate e ai suoi successori ogni mese di agosto al
                        monastero il censo annuale di 6 denari d’argento. Se non rispetteranno i
                        suddetti impegni, promettono con i loro eredi di versare all’abate e ai suoi
                        successori la pena di una libbra d’oro. Auctum predicto monasterio <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">territurio</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/154">Rosellense</geogName>. + Ego
                        Stefan(us) abb(as) in unc libelu a me facto subscripsi. Testimoni: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rodelandus">Rollandi</name></persName> filio
                        bone memorie <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Buchulus"
                            >Buchuli</name></persName>; <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Gherardus">Gherardi</name></persName> filio bone memorie
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Teutius">Teutii</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Teutius">Teutio</name></persName>
                        filio suo. Scrive <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Petrus"
                                >Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scriptor.</ab>
                        </div>
